Let's get some hats out here.

01:20:14.643 --> 01:20:15.979
- Alright some hats.

01:20:15.979 --> 01:20:18.081
A blue one for the man in blue.

01:20:18.081 --> 01:20:19.548
- Need blue, you do?

01:20:19.548 --> 01:20:23.019
Okay.

